Class ProjectsRepository

Object
ProjectsRepository
All Implemented Interfaces:
IRepository<Project,String>
public class ProjectsRepository extends Object implements IRepository<Project,String>
This entity class is a repository for managing Project entities. Uses Project Name (String) as the ID. Assumes Project Names are unique.
